name: [LoRa]  Pteridophyte/ 早蕨 Concept (With multires noise version)
description:
※A experimental LoRa model trained by a friend with multires noise.

This is a LoRa model that trained by 60+ img generated with NijiV5,and it's the multires noise version.

This model can generate a powerful background style with a complex pattern similar to that of ferns.

weight 0.8-1.0 maybe generates better imgs.

It's a experimental work,Hope you found it usefulミ(・・)ミ
